Package semsim.model.computational.datastructures

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DataStructure
    This class represents a symbolic element in a simulation model that is assigned some computational value during simulation.
    Decimal
    A DataStructure that is assigned a decimal value during simulation.
    MappableVariable
    A MappableVariable is a Decimal that has a specified input/output designation within the context of a FunctionalSubmodel.
    MMLchoice
    This class maps to the JSim-specific data structure called a "choice" variable.
    SBMLFunctionOutput
    Class for working with SBML-style function definitions
    SemSimInteger
    A DataStructure that is assigned an integer value during simulation.
